      • LogLineBuffer

        public LogLineBuffer(int maxCapacity,
             float loadFactor)
        Ctor
        Parameters:
        maxCapacity - - the maximum capacity (entries of ILogLines) of this buffer.
        loadFactor - - the percentage of maxCapacity the buffer is filled after it has to be shrink on reaching its maxCapacity. For example if the maxCapa is 100 and the loadFactor 0.75 the buffer will contain at least 75 ILogLines after reaching the limit of 100.
